<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="60800000t" end="85600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">人们称我为「魔王」</p>
<p begin="89200000t" end="137000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">过去的友人 已经不再视我为人类</p>
<p begin="142500000t" end="185800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">于是我开始祈求败北</p>
<p begin="194700000t" end="220900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">因为只要他们看见我狼狈地输掉</p>
<p begin="220900000t" end="256500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">就会把我视为跟他们一样的人类吧</p>
<p begin="263600000t" end="301800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">然而 有希望打败我的敌人都走了</p>
<p begin="301800000t" end="338300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">我的人生似乎进入了死局</p>
<p begin="510600000t" end="527500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">不过 到了来世</p>
<p begin="527500000t" end="555900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">或许我就能享受不同的命运了吧</p>
<p begin="633300000t" end="658000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">那我就 转生吧</p>
<p begin="658000000t" end="662600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">哔哩哔哩译制<br />Translated by bilibili</p>
<p begin="761300000t" end="800900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">在我们的儿子「亚德·梅特奥尔」的生日之际</p>
<p begin="808800000t" end="833300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">我们要感谢神祖 魔王巴尔巴托斯陛下</p>
<p begin="833300000t" end="859200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">以及女王陛下的恩泽</p>
<p begin="869900000t" end="891300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">亚德 生日快乐</p>
<p begin="897300000t" end="916200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">亚德也到十岁了啊</p>
<p begin="920500000t" end="942800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">你出生那天我还记忆犹新呢</p>
<p begin="942800000t" end="963900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">时间过得真快啊</p>
<p begin="969800000t" end="1003500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">你是我们的骄傲 亚德</p>
<p begin="1008200000t" end="1038800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">谢谢你们 父亲 母亲</p>
<p begin="1041700000t" end="1075100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">比起爸爸我 你倒是更像卡拉 真有男子汉气概</p>
<p begin="1075100000t" end="1106800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">真会说话 亚德之所以文武双全</p>
<p begin="1106800000t" end="1130500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">是因为你这个爹啊 杰克</p>
<p begin="1135700000t" end="1165900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">于是 曾经那个人称魔王的我</p>
<p begin="1169400000t" end="1191300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">出生在一个稀松平常的乡下小镇家庭</p>
<p begin="1194600000t" end="1237900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">父母的优点只有关系和睦 是对随处可见的夫妇</p>
<p begin="1243400000t" end="1263500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">他们的独生子便是我 「亚德·梅特奥尔」</p>
<p begin="1291400000t" end="1301600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">也不知算幸运还是不幸</p>
<p begin="1304800000t" end="1326900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">当代的魔法和学问</p>
<p begin="1329600000t" end="1362500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">相较于我所处的时代似乎严重衰退 水平很低</p>
<p begin="1375200000t" end="1395700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">另外 我的健康 体力</p>
<p begin="1399100000t" end="1424600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">还有运动神经还算不错</p>
<p begin="1428000000t" end="1452900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">也没费多大劲就练好了武艺</p>
<p begin="1472600000t" end="1484800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">好了 亚德</p>
<p begin="1484800000t" end="1503100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">你今后有什么打算呢</p>
<p begin="1507400000t" end="1537300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">都到十岁了 也该开始反抗父母了</p>
<p begin="1542700000t" end="1580700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">你这岁数 该开始思考将来和自己的梦想了吧</p>
<p begin="1585700000t" end="1599000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">梦想吗</p>
<p begin="1624300000t" end="1655600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">没错 我有梦想 有野心</p>
<p begin="1664100000t" end="1680300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">自我转生后 转眼已过去十年</p>
<p begin="1683300000t" end="1742400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">随着智力和体力的成长 我已经有资格跟人结下友谊了</p>
<p begin="1752300000t" end="1778400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">我要找到不会畏惧我的人</p>
<p begin="1778400000t" end="1806700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">结交可以平起平坐的朋友</p>
<p begin="1806700000t" end="1825000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">好耶 我赢了</p>
<p begin="1828200000t" end="1840600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">好赖啊</p>
<p begin="1840600000t" end="1857100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">一不小心又赢了</p>
<p begin="1864100000t" end="1884300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">为什么你这么强啊</p>
<p begin="1891400000t" end="1908200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">快来找我说话</p>
<p begin="1912100000t" end="1956300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">换作前世 跟魔王直接对话是大忌</p>
<p begin="1962900000t" end="1982900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">然而时代变了</p>
<p begin="1982900000t" end="2007400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">如今我只是一介村民A</p>
<p begin="2013100000t" end="2035100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">不必顾忌 快来吧</p>
<p begin="2038600000t" end="2055600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">我可以陪你们聊个够</p>
<p begin="2075300000t" end="2085900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">喂 看那里</p>
<p begin="2104800000t" end="2115200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">他在干嘛啊</p>
<p begin="2142900000t" end="2156400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">感觉好可怕</p>
<p begin="2156400000t" end="2164900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">走吧</p>
<p begin="2164900000t" end="2172900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">嗯</p>
<p begin="2196200000t" end="2218400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">我都摆出来者不拒的态度等着了</p>
<p begin="2222100000t" end="2244200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">为什么 为什么要跑掉</p>
<p begin="2251800000t" end="2285100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">是因为我有着转生也隐藏不住的威严</p>
<p begin="2288100000t" end="2324000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">干涉了他们的深层心理 阻止他们接近我吗</p>
<p begin="2341800000t" end="2359100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">既然如此 我就只能不断前进</p>
<p begin="2359100000t" end="2380900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">等待不如行动</p>
<p begin="2449400000t" end="2467500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">好大的压力</p>
<p begin="2470600000t" end="2480000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">怎么可能</p>
<p begin="2480000000t" end="2530700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">哪怕在跟诸神决战前 我心里都没有丝毫恐惧</p>
<p begin="2538000000t" end="2555800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">现在竟然紧张得肚子疼</p>
<p begin="2672000000t" end="2697600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">能把我逼到这一步 真是不简单</p>
<p begin="2703700000t" end="2739200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">不过 我好歹也是曾被奉为魔王的男人</p>
<p begin="2742800000t" end="2769400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">面对这微不足道的危机 我怎么能退缩</p>
<p begin="2786400000t" end="2820200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">你…你们几个 给我转过来</p>
<p begin="2838400000t" end="2864100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">乖…乖乖听话就好</p>
<p begin="2868200000t" end="2885300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">值…值得称赞</p>
<p begin="2889900000t" end="2923500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">你…你们几个 那个…</p>
<p begin="2933400000t" end="2942000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">就是…</p>
<p begin="2946000000t" end="2953900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">请说</p>
<p begin="2958100000t" end="2987700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">那个 就是说…</p>
<p begin="3004300000t" end="3022300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">当…当我的朋友吧</p>
<p begin="3022300000t" end="3046400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">若是答应 就送你们一半世界好了</p>
<p begin="3057100000t" end="3077100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">说了…我说出来了</p>
<p begin="3106300000t" end="3119400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">咦？等…</p>
<p begin="3189500000t" end="3212600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">我是魔王巴尔巴托斯</p>
<p begin="3218400000t" end="3253200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">征服了诸多国家 消灭了众多英雄</p>
<p begin="3253200000t" end="3267700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">歼灭了诸神</p>
<p begin="3277400000t" end="3319400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">然而 现在连人类的小孩都不听我的话</p>
<p begin="3348500000t" end="3375700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">为什么 为什么不服从我的命令</p>
<p begin="3391400000t" end="3421600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">我都主动搭话了 还提出了交易</p>
<p begin="3447200000t" end="3474900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">你们还想要什么啊</p>
<p begin="3474900000t" end="3493000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">可恶 真搞不懂</p>
<p begin="3566400000t" end="3581200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">还是就此收手吧</p>
<p begin="3585600000t" end="3610000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">影响到这一带的生态系统就不好了</p>
<p begin="3624200000t" end="3665100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">可是 我还能做什么呢</p>
<p begin="3741900000t" end="3760100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">你怎么了 亚德</p>
<p begin="3767500000t" end="3788600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">怎么无精打采的</p>
<p begin="3807800000t" end="3847000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">你该不会连村长我都不认识了吧</p>
<p begin="3853800000t" end="3867800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">奥尔海德卿</p>
<p begin="3910900000t" end="3923900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">朋友吗</p>
<p begin="3927500000t" end="3969000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">到底要怎样才能建立起友好关系呢</p>
<p begin="3978500000t" end="4007500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">我把能想到的办法都用上了</p>
<p begin="4012100000t" end="4027200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">感觉已经束手无策了</p>
<p begin="4035200000t" end="4068400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">教你一个简单的方法吧</p>
<p begin="4071000000t" end="4090800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">啊？是什么咒语啊？</p>
<p begin="4094200000t" end="4118100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">还是高深的政治战略？</p>
<p begin="4121400000t" end="4131900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">不是的</p>
<p begin="4137800000t" end="4169600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">无论什么时候 无论面对什么人</p>
<p begin="4169600000t" end="4203900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">都要表现得平易近人 不忘绅士精神</p>
<p begin="4214900000t" end="4260400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">如此一来 自然就能结交到朋友了</p>
<p begin="4264200000t" end="4292200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">平易近人…绅士精神…</p>
<p begin="4299100000t" end="4315500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">我懂了</p>
<p begin="4315500000t" end="4335300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">不愧是奥尔海德卿</p>
<p begin="4343100000t" end="4356200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">那么 亚德</p>
<p begin="4360100000t" end="4380300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">说到朋友 我女儿…</p>
<p begin="4380300000t" end="4406900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">多谢建议 我这就去试试</p>
<p begin="4466300000t" end="4481300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">身为我的儿子</p>
<p begin="4485800000t" end="4523700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">有时候却很奇…不可思议啊</p>
<p begin="4530900000t" end="4563500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">话说回来 维斯 你刚才说的那事…</p>
<p begin="4583700000t" end="4601100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">国政方面的问题还好说</p>
<p begin="4604200000t" end="4631000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">这方面我就一筹莫展了</p>
<p begin="4635700000t" end="4650300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">真是太惭愧了</p>
<p begin="4655000000t" end="4693200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">我明白你很担心 我们也一样</p>
<p begin="4707800000t" end="4732000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">在下亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="4732000000t" end="4776200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">可否与我成为肝胆相照的总角之交呢</p>
<p begin="4817100000t" end="4837300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">恕我冒昧</p>
<p begin="4837300000t" end="4868400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">敢问几位美丽动人的姑娘</p>
<p begin="4868400000t" end="4893200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">可否赏脸跟我做朋友</p>
<p begin="4952400000t" end="4982900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">干脆把这鬼世界毁了吧</p>
<p begin="5068700000t" end="5082800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">不行 要冷静</p>
<p begin="5082800000t" end="5100300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">你得冷静下来 亚德·梅特奥尔</p>
<p begin="5113400000t" end="5135600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">破坏和混沌什么都创造不了</p>
<p begin="5135600000t" end="5152090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">我前世不是切身体会过了吗</p>
<p begin="5189790000t" end="5216600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">不好 又乱泄愤了</p>
<p begin="5216600000t" end="5236090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">可恶</p>
<p begin="5236090000t" end="5261300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">讨厌讨厌讨厌 讨厌死了</p>
<p begin="5265300000t" end="5293900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">听这声音…是位尚且年幼的少女</p>
<p begin="5360300000t" end="5371900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">出什么事了</p>
<p begin="5448900000t" end="5477400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">灼炎招来 随我怒火</p>
<p begin="5477400000t" end="5494600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">烧毁一切</p>
<p begin="5562600000t" end="5575500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">怎么回事</p>
<p begin="5579100000t" end="5601600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">敌人不过是只远古狼而已</p>
<p begin="5605800000t" end="5629600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">怎么可能陷入苦战</p>
<p begin="5654000000t" end="5671400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">她是在解闷吧</p>
<p begin="5685100000t" end="5710100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">当时的欺凌和暗地里的坏话</p>
<p begin="5713600000t" end="5741600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">导致我女儿彻底关闭了心扉</p>
<p begin="5747500000t" end="5779200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">甚至都不怎么跟我这个父亲说话了</p>
<p begin="5784300000t" end="5813000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">不过 我可以理解她闭门不出的心情</p>
<p begin="5817600000t" end="5848800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">毕竟血脉是无法改变的</p>
<p begin="5856700000t" end="5887600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">比起王都 这里人也不多</p>
<p begin="5891100000t" end="5910300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">确实回来更好</p>
<p begin="5918000000t" end="5935600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">但愿如此吧</p>
<p begin="5954300000t" end="5972100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">雷鸣凝聚于我手</p>
<p begin="5975300000t" end="6007200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">天雷啊 倾注于我眼前之敌</p>
<p begin="6165700000t" end="6172900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">莉迪娅</p>
<p begin="6205400000t" end="6236800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">对不起 我没想吓你</p>
<p begin="6270800000t" end="6283300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">你想干嘛</p>
<p begin="6307300000t" end="6315900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">那个…</p>
<p begin="6321500000t" end="6352400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">我…我看了你刚才的战斗</p>
<p begin="6355200000t" end="6369000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">实在是精彩</p>
<p begin="6369000000t" end="6402600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">年纪轻轻就如此厉害的人可不多见啊</p>
<p begin="6414800000t" end="6424400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">糟了</p>
<p begin="6424400000t" end="6452800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">她是那种不爱炫耀力量的人吗</p>
<p begin="6457300000t" end="6481900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">一听就很假的赞美会适得其反</p>
<p begin="6490900000t" end="6499500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">既然如此…</p>
<p begin="6511400000t" end="6535100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">恕…恕我直言</p>
<p begin="6538700000t" end="6556600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">你还差得远</p>
<p begin="6562400000t" end="6585600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">应该还有钻研的余地</p>
<p begin="6604400000t" end="6627500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">糟了 说得太重了吗</p>
<p begin="6631600000t" end="6659700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">夸也不行 贬也不行</p>
<p begin="6663000000t" end="6673800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">我该怎么办</p>
<p begin="6698600000t" end="6710500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">不嫌弃的话</p>
<p begin="6721600000t" end="6754700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">可以跟我…做朋友吗</p>
<p begin="6769500000t" end="6779300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">糟了</p>
<p begin="6779300000t" end="6815800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">本该慢慢拉近距离 结果直接切入正题了</p>
<p begin="6822400000t" end="6837100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">彻底完蛋了</p>
<p begin="6855000000t" end="6867400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">做朋友？</p>
<p begin="6879500000t" end="6887400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">不对</p>
<p begin="6895500000t" end="6915200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">第一次引出反应了</p>
<p begin="6922400000t" end="6939800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">搞不好这样能行？</p>
<p begin="6944200000t" end="6971400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">单刀直入奏效了吗</p>
<p begin="6980900000t" end="6994300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">对 做朋友</p>
<p begin="6999500000t" end="7023900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">我觉得我们很像</p>
<p begin="7028600000t" end="7061800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">我认为我们可以相互理解 共同进步</p>
<p begin="7061800000t" end="7084000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">必定能结下美好的友情</p>
<p begin="7084000000t" end="7092900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">所以…</p>
<p begin="7092900000t" end="7103400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">开什么玩笑</p>
<p begin="7109600000t" end="7116700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">啊？</p>
<p begin="7128600000t" end="7140300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">理解？</p>
<p begin="7150800000t" end="7161300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">怎么可能</p>
<p begin="7164900000t" end="7190900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">你了解我什么啊</p>
<p begin="7238700000t" end="7248900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">哭了？</p>
<p begin="7258200000t" end="7266600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">为什么…</p>
<p begin="7288800000t" end="7312300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">今后还请继续关照</p>
<p begin="7315700000t" end="7323500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">嗯</p>
<p begin="7326900000t" end="7337600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">这是当然的</p>
<p begin="7342400000t" end="7350800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">爸爸</p>
<p begin="7384800000t" end="7404100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">我还是受不了这穷乡僻壤</p>
<p begin="7404100000t" end="7431500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">伊莉娜 你受不了…为什么？</p>
<p begin="7434900000t" end="7452100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">奥尔海德卿</p>
<p begin="7457900000t" end="7473300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">我按照你的建议…</p>
<p begin="7551200000t" end="7561200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">这是…</p>
<p begin="7573100000t" end="7582800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">命运？</p>
<p begin="7598500000t" end="7611700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">别过来啊</p>
<p begin="7611700000t" end="7629500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">你好啊 伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="7629500000t" end="7650600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">你今天的气色也很好啊</p>
<p begin="7654800000t" end="7678800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">我不记得跟你说过名字啊</p>
<p begin="7678800000t" end="7701300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">是你父亲告诉我的</p>
<p begin="7704400000t" end="7731100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">话说回来 世界真小啊</p>
<p begin="7731100000t" end="7769100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">想不到我父母的好友奥尔海德卿的千金</p>
<p begin="7769100000t" end="7783600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">竟然就是伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="7783600000t" end="7818000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">我们要不要效仿父母 也做朋友啊</p>
<p begin="7821700000t" end="7832400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">恶心</p>
<p begin="7836100000t" end="7870900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">我表现得平易近人 不忘绅士精神</p>
<p begin="7877000000t" end="7906900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">这样一来 应该早晚能培养出友情</p>
<p begin="7918200000t" end="7943300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">生日快乐 伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="7948300000t" end="7980600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">我准备了你喜欢的玫瑰花束</p>
<p begin="7987500000t" end="8008600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">你怎么知道我喜欢什么啊</p>
<p begin="8013500000t" end="8041400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">我对你无所不知哦</p>
<p begin="8041400000t" end="8064000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">包括你身上有几颗痣</p>
<p begin="8101000000t" end="8109300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">恶心</p>
<p begin="8124600000t" end="8143900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">这是跟她成为朋友的机会</p>
<p begin="8150700000t" end="8170300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">我怎么可能放过</p>
<p begin="8312500000t" end="8329800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">你怎么会在这里</p>
<p begin="8337700000t" end="8371800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">因为我知道你喜欢找魔物泄愤</p>
<p begin="8379300000t" end="8399200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">我来接你了</p>
<p begin="8486200000t" end="8512300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">月色真美啊 伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="8512300000t" end="8520800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">好快</p>
<p begin="8526100000t" end="8562100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">那清澈的光芒 犹如银白的湖泊</p>
<p begin="8566000000t" end="8589500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">而你宛若月亮</p>
<p begin="8589500000t" end="8613100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">不 是比月亮更美</p>
<p begin="8613100000t" end="8621500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">恶心</p>
<p begin="8652000000t" end="8673200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">我绝不会放弃</p>
<p begin="8703600000t" end="8745700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">「问好战术」目前没有显著的效果</p>
<p begin="8751100000t" end="8780300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">贿赂和礼品似乎也很难奏效</p>
<p begin="8787600000t" end="8814300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">即使我想靠诗歌和音乐营造气氛</p>
<p begin="8817700000t" end="8845700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">她也总是扭头就跑 没什么效果</p>
<p begin="8855200000t" end="8869300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">剩下的战术是…</p>
<p begin="8881500000t" end="8905000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">貌似在前世也碰到过类似的情况</p>
<p begin="8912600000t" end="8956900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">为了讨好对方 我想方设法表现</p>
<p begin="8960900000t" end="8973700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">对方却无动于衷…</p>
<p begin="9110800000t" end="9122300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">这是怎么了</p>
<p begin="9258900000t" end="9267400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">父亲</p>
<p begin="9267400000t" end="9290800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">亚德 快进屋里避难</p>
<p begin="9295000000t" end="9314400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">这状况是怎么回事</p>
<p begin="9314400000t" end="9337100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">山上的地牢核心失控了</p>
<p begin="9343800000t" end="9366800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">杰克 来帮帮我</p>
<p begin="9366800000t" end="9393600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">伊莉娜…伊莉娜在山上</p>
<p begin="9396300000t" end="9405900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">- 你说什么？<br />- 什么？</p>
<p begin="9409800000t" end="9433400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">白天出门后到现在都没回来</p>
<p begin="9449500000t" end="9462600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">都怪我</p>
<p begin="9462600000t" end="9498200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">都怪我缠着她 她才会躲到山上去</p>
<p begin="9509900000t" end="9526500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">交给我吧 奥尔海德卿</p>
<p begin="9529600000t" end="9558000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">我一定会把她带回来的</p>
<p begin="9562600000t" end="9572800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">亚德</p>
<p begin="9572800000t" end="9587600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">你说什么呢</p>
<p begin="9587600000t" end="9594900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">我走了</p>
<p begin="9635800000t" end="9645200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">那是…</p>
<p begin="9681100000t" end="9715000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">这可真是个漂亮的小姑娘</p>
<p begin="9741600000t" end="9773800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">预料之外的危机吓坏你了吗</p>
<p begin="9777100000t" end="9806800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">本想蹂躏魔物 结果形势逆转了</p>
<p begin="9806800000t" end="9829700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">什…什么形势逆转啊</p>
<p begin="9829700000t" end="9847700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">区区哥布林</p>
<p begin="9847700000t" end="9880300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">那你就好好抵抗 让我找点乐子吧</p>
<p begin="9920100000t" end="9946900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">怎么了 不求救吗</p>
<p begin="9946900000t" end="9973800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">大喊家人和朋友的名字呗</p>
<p begin="9978000000t" end="9997800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">才没有呢</p>
<p begin="10005700000t" end="10026400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">听说伊莉娜是怪物</p>
<p begin="10031200000t" end="10049000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">伊莉娜好可怕</p>
<p begin="10063500000t" end="10111600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">好可怕 好可怕 好可怕…</p>
<p begin="10143100000t" end="10162400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">算了 随你便吧</p>
<p begin="10165800000t" end="10183000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">反正活着也没意思</p>
<p begin="10188200000t" end="10206600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">搞什么 真没劲</p>
<p begin="10206600000t" end="10233800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">小的们 这姑娘任由你们处置了</p>
<p begin="10310600000t" end="10329600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">不…不要…</p>
<p begin="10358100000t" end="10384090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">救命啊</p>
<p begin="10512900000t" end="10525700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">亚…亚德？</p>
<p begin="10532900000t" end="10558200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">你终于肯叫我的名字了啊</p>
<p begin="10558200000t" end="10568500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="10574200000t" end="10589400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">为…为什么…</p>
<p begin="10596700000t" end="10621300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">当然是为了救你啊</p>
<p begin="10627100000t" end="10661300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">不过 欺负弱者可不好啊</p>
<p begin="10661300000t" end="10684700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">泄愤要适可而止</p>
<p begin="10684700000t" end="10706600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">欺负弱者？</p>
<p begin="10706600000t" end="10720700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">别过来 快跑</p>
<p begin="10720700000t" end="10734500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">你也会死的</p>
<p begin="10739700000t" end="10750300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">怎么可能</p>
<p begin="10840800000t" end="10856300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">这…这是？</p>
<p begin="10860800000t" end="10909000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">别想碰伊莉娜小姐 也别想碰我一根汗毛</p>
<p begin="10909000000t" end="10938100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">就两个人类 还想翻天不成</p>
<p begin="10938100000t" end="10950500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">喂 小的们</p>
<p begin="10955900000t" end="10974100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">别干徒劳的事</p>
<p begin="10978300000t" end="11004100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">现在逃走 不是不能放你们一马</p>
<p begin="11004100000t" end="11015800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">给我上</p>
<p begin="11190300000t" end="11211100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">为自己做的选择后悔吧</p>
<p begin="11312200000t" end="11337700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">亚德那小子还没回来啊</p>
<p begin="11341200000t" end="11358100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">他应该没问题吧</p>
<p begin="11358100000t" end="11365400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">啊？</p>
<p begin="11368900000t" end="11403100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">亚德向我保证过 会带伊莉娜回来</p>
<p begin="11406900000t" end="11427500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">所以伊莉娜不会有事的</p>
<p begin="11447000000t" end="11470600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">说起来 那小子的飞行魔法…</p>
<p begin="11475800000t" end="11499300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">该不会是「失落技能」吧</p>
<p begin="11550800000t" end="11570500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">伊莉娜小姐 没事吧</p>
<p begin="11596900000t" end="11615700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">为…为什么…</p>
<p begin="11643300000t" end="11657400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">为什么要救我</p>
<p begin="11665100000t" end="11681900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">我想死啊</p>
<p begin="11689900000t" end="11715700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">别说这么令人难过的话</p>
<p begin="11720400000t" end="11731100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">不介意的话…</p>
<p begin="11731100000t" end="11761800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">不要 你怎么可能理解我的感受</p>
<p begin="11766700000t" end="11783300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">又孤单又寂寞…</p>
<p begin="11788600000t" end="11813300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">又痛苦…又伤心…</p>
<p begin="11818100000t" end="11828700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">请等一下</p>
<p begin="11832900000t" end="11846400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">究竟是出于怎样的原因</p>
<p begin="11846400000t" end="11881500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">让你产生了这种感情 我不得而知</p>
<p begin="11888700000t" end="11920300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">但是 要说孤独带来的痛苦</p>
<p begin="11920300000t" end="11942200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">我比任何人都理解哦</p>
<p begin="11949900000t" end="11990500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">正因如此 我很想跟你做朋友</p>
<p begin="11990500000t" end="12022300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">骗人 你肯定早晚会背叛我的</p>
<p begin="12025700000t" end="12042500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">就跟我以前的朋友一样</p>
<p begin="12047000000t" end="12059300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">我不会背叛的</p>
<p begin="12064800000t" end="12099800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">我再也不会 绝对不会背叛朋友了</p>
<p begin="12112800000t" end="12129600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">因为我曾经…</p>
<p begin="12134500000t" end="12159900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">背叛过好朋友</p>
<p begin="12168600000t" end="12202900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">所以这一次 我绝不会伤害你</p>
<p begin="12202900000t" end="12219600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">想跟你结下永恒的友谊</p>
<p begin="12224900000t" end="12266300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">不过 我的性格肯定比那个人更差</p>
<p begin="12266300000t" end="12275900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">我不在乎</p>
<p begin="12282200000t" end="12313800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">还…还很任性 也不聪明…</p>
<p begin="12317000000t" end="12333500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">跟我在一起很无聊的</p>
<p begin="12339900000t" end="12354500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">没这回事</p>
<p begin="12359300000t" end="12402600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">其实能跟你聊天 我感到非常开心</p>
<p begin="12410900000t" end="12451500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">你早晚…早晚会讨厌我的</p>
<p begin="12460400000t" end="12470600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">这不可能</p>
<p begin="12480300000t" end="12506500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">可…可是我 其实…</p>
<p begin="12559800000t" end="12587600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">你真的愿意跟我这种人做朋友吗</p>
<p begin="12590600000t" end="12602200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">发生什么事都愿意吗</p>
<p begin="12609000000t" end="12638900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">绝对不会背叛我 不会讨厌我吗</p>
<p begin="12642700000t" end="12664300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">我向魔王巴尔巴托斯发誓</p>
<p begin="12716700000t" end="12731400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">向巴尔巴托斯发誓…</p>
<p begin="12742300000t" end="12770500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">今后还请多多指教 伊莉娜小姐</p>
<p begin="12770500000t" end="12794400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">请…请多指教 亚德</p>
<p begin="12807500000t" end="12836900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">于是 转生为村民A的</p>
<p begin="12840400000t" end="12864500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">史上最强魔王巴尔巴托斯</p>
<p begin="12869300000t" end="12885000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">结交了终生之友</p>
<p begin="12888000000t" end="12917000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">每天都过着幸福的生活</p>
<p begin="12917000000t" end="12925200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">可喜可贺 可喜可贺</p>
<p begin="12925200000t" end="12932900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">(数年后)<br />可喜可贺 可喜可贺</p>
<p begin="12932900000t" end="12949600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">(数年后)</p>
<p begin="13003000000t" end="13019700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">亚德 早上好</p>
<p begin="13044600000t" end="13097300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">真可爱 我的朋友简直是天使…</p>
<p begin="13135000000t" end="13146600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">伊莉娜小姐？</p>
<p begin="13150400000t" end="13170000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">一…一个妙龄女子</p>
<p begin="13170000000t" end="13200300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">竟然闯进男人的房间 成何体统</p>
<p begin="13200300000t" end="13229600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">非但如此 还躺在同一张床上</p>
<p begin="13233200000t" end="13263000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">我说 亚德 去魔法学园上学吧</p>
<p begin="13286000000t" end="13292400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">啊？</p>
<p begin="13457500000t" end="13490300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">足以融化孤独的呼声</p>
<p begin="13490300000t" end="13528600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">究竟来自于何人？</p>
<p begin="13534700000t" end="13578900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">向往着温暖 我出发了。</p>
<p begin="13578900000t" end="13596300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">再来，再来，再来！</p>
<p begin="13601100000t" end="13618100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">咏唱 交个朋友</p>
<p begin="13618100000t" end="13634500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">解除 扑克脸</p>
<p begin="13634500000t" end="13665900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">平起平坐的坦诚交谈</p>
<p begin="13667500000t" end="13685100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">打破墙壁吧 用转移魔法</p>
<p begin="13685100000t" end="13701100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">瞬间便融洽相处</p>
<p begin="13701100000t" end="13717200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">共鸣之和谐 打破孤独</p>
<p begin="13717200000t" end="13730900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">精准无比 太完美了吧？</p>
<p begin="13730900000t" end="13794400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">沉默寡言的挑战者 迈出第一步</p>
<p begin="13794400000t" end="13848300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">生涩的自己也要抱紧</p>
<p begin="13852200000t" end="13886300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">一起开始尝试！就是现在 尝试！</p>
<p begin="13889600000t" end="13927700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">向奇迹发起挑战吧</p>
<p begin="13927700000t" end="13968000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">将无敌的心情连结到底</p>
<p begin="13968000000t" end="13985000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">放马过来 放马过来</p>
<p begin="13985000000t" end="14018800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">鼓足干劲 尝试！发展超乎想像</p>
<p begin="14021300000t" end="14053100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">点燃勇气</p>
<p begin="14053100000t" end="14092600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">即使现在相隔遥远</p>
<p begin="14092600000t" end="14127000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">有朝一日 也必定能相互理解</p>
<p begin="14127000000t" end="14142700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">做我的朋友！！！</p>
